# Only publish what's needed for npm install:
# - package.json (automatic)
# - scripts/install.js (postinstall)
# - bin/ (created at install time)
# - README.md (automatic)
# - LICENSE (automatic)

# Exclude everything else
internal/
cmd/
web/
.github/
screenshots/
*.go
go.mod
go.sum
Makefile
*.md
!README.md
!LICENSE
.claude/
coverage*
cli*
*.html
*.txt
*.out
